title: Cape Lookout National Seashore: Homecoming Photos
body: Explore This Park    Plan Your Visit     Things To Do     Special Events     Portsmouth Homecoming     Homecoming Photos                  Portsmouth Homecoming Photos                    Portsmouth Homecoming   16 Photos  Every other year, the Friends of Portsmouth Island and Cape Lookout National Seashore host an old-fashioned homecoming in Portsmouth Village. Everyone is welcome to join in this celebration of history and community.
